reviewText: The description was misleading, there are not three items as described, there are two.  There is a CD in a card holder and a DVD in a card holder, there is not also a birthday card as was described.  I think the description needs to be changed to honestly reflect what is in the package.
This was the perfect gift for a friend who turned 60. Great collection of songs and happenings from the year he was born in a high-quality greeting card.
